WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Build a memory ladder to learn faster.

00:04.200 --> 00:08.000
Anchor new ideas to something you already know.

00:08.200 --> 00:12.000
Chunk information into 3–5 item groups.

00:12.200 --> 00:16.000
Create a quick story or visual hook for each chunk.

00:16.200 --> 00:20.000
Use spaced repetition: 1 day, 3 days, 1 week.

00:20.200 --> 00:24.000
Active recall beats re‑reading—test yourself briefly.

00:24.200 --> 00:28.000
Refine the ladder by collapsing weak links.

00:28.200 --> 00:32.000
Keep cues short, vivid, and personally meaningful.
